ivities.\n|-\n| [[File:RENEA.svg|center|33px]] || '''[[RENEA]]'''<br>The Department of Neutralization of Armed Elements is the main [[counter-terrorism]] and critical incident response unit.\n|}\n\n==Equipment==\n* [[Glock 34]]\n* [[TT-33]]\n* [[Beretta 92]]\n* [[Beretta PX4 Storm]]\n* [[Beretta ARX 160]]\n* [[HS Produkt VHS]]\n* [[Heckler & Koch MP5]]\n* [[Heckler & Koch MP7]]\n* [[AK-47]]\n*[[Sako TRG M10]]\n*[[Land Rover Defender|Land Rover Defend]] [[4x4]] [[Turkey]] has donated armored vehicles<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://armyrecognition.com/january_2020_global_defense_security_army_news_industry/turkey_has_donated_armored_vehicles_and_security_equipment_to_albania_police.html|website=armyrecognition.com|access-date=2020-01-18}}</ref>\n\n== Directors == \n{| cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"3\" style=\"border:1px solid #000000; font-size:88%; line-height: 1.5em;\"\n|-\n|'''{{underline|No.}}'''\n|'''{{underline|Name}}'''\n|colspan=\"2\"|<center>'''{{underline|Term in office}}'''</center>\n|-\n|align=center|1\n|Halim Gostivari\n|13 January 1913\n|24 May 1913\n|-\n|align=center|2\n|Feim Mezhgorani\n|24 May 1913\n|30 January 1914\n|-\n|align=center|3\n|[[Hil Mosi]]\n|1 February 1914\n|30 March 1914\n|-\n|align=center|4\n|Veli Vasjari\n|1 April 1914\n|30 June 1914\n|-\n|align=center|5\n|Sulejman K\u00ebr\u00e7iku\n|2 October 1914\n|27 January 1916\n|-\n|align=center|6\n|Halim Gostivari\n|28 August 1919\n|17 December 1920\n|-\n|align=center|7\n|Ahmet Sinani\n|17 December 1920\n|10 January 1922\n|-\n|align=center|8\n|Veli Vasjari\n|11 January 1922\n|22 April 1922\n|-\n|align=center|9\n|Halim Gostivari\n|22 April 1922\n|21 August 1922\n|-\n|align=center|10\n|Musa \u00c7elepia\n|21 August 1922\n|26 December 1922\n|-\n|align=center|11\n|Hamza Isaraj\n|10 December 1924\n|25 December 1924\n|-\n|align=center|12\n|Qazim Bodinaku\n|24 February 1926\n|7 July 1926\n|-\n|align=center|13\n|Rrustem Ymeri\n|20 December 1926\n|1927\n|-\n|align=center|14\n|[[Hil Mosi]]\n|3 September 19